OL,3,CFantasy world flat gets Grade II
OL,4,Clisted status
OL,6,FA rented flat that was transformed
OL,7,Finto a fantasy world by its artistic
OL,8,Ftenant has been given Grade II listing
OL,9,Fafter volunteers stepped in to save it.
OL,11,FThe ground-floor interior, hidden
OL,12,Fbehind the front door of a semi-
OL,13,Fdetached house in , Wirral, was
OL,14,Fdecorated by Ron Gittins, who created
OL,15,Ffireplaces in the shape of a lion and
OL,16,Fa minotaur, crafted a Roman altar in
OL,17,Fthe kitchen and painted Egyptian,
OL,18,FGreek and marine murals floor to
OL,19,Fceiling.
