OL,6,FMr Gittins only allowed a handful of
OL,7,Fpeople inside the home, where he lived
OL,8,Ffor more than 30 years, but when his
OL,9,Fniece Jan Williams visited following
OL,10,Fhis death in 2019 she dedicated
OL,11,Fherself to saving the flat, known as
OL,12,FRon's Place.
OL,14,FNow, Mr Gittins' work has become the
OL,15,Ffirst example of Outsider Art ` a term
OL,16,Fused for work done by those without
OL,17,Fconventional training ` to be granted
OL,18,FGrade II listing by the Department for
OL,19,FCulture, Media and Sport (DCMS),
OL,20,Ffollowing the advice of Historic
OL,21,FEngland.
