OL,6,FFormer to save the flat, said: "A
OL,7,Fsmall number of people on this planet
OL,8,Fhave known for a while that Ron's
OL,9,FPlace is a very special place ` but
OL,10,Ffrom now on it is official: Ron's
OL,11,FPlace has been given listed status!
OL,13,F"The work of one unique gentleman in
OL,14,Fthe north of England has been
OL,15,Frecognised nationally. Globally even.
OL,16,FHallelujah!"
OL,18,FMs Williams said originally she and
OL,19,Ffellow volunteers applied to have the
OL,20,Fproperty listed to "ward off evil" and
OL,21,Fput developers off buying the building.
