OL,6,FBut, a donation last year meant the
OL,7,Fgroup, as Wirral Arts and Culture
OL,8,FCommunity Land Trust, was able to buy
OL,9,Fthe home at auction and now hope to
OL,10,Fuse it to inspire other artists.
OL,12,FMs Williams, who is also an artist and
OL,13,Fruns the Caravan Gallery, said: "We
OL,14,Fhave always had the idea of a holistic
OL,15,Fhouse of art. I'm sure that's what Ron
OL,16,Fwould have wanted, and having the
OL,17,Flisting gives us a lot more
OL,18,Fcredibility."
