OL,6,FShe said she believed her uncle, who
OL,7,Fdied aged 79, would be "over the moon"
OL,8,Fto know his work had been listed.
OL,10,FShe added: "He was really proud of it.
OL,11,FIt's sad because when I was going
OL,12,Fthrough his stuff I found a postcard
OL,13,Fhe'd written to me saying 'I can't
OL,14,Fwait to show you what I've done'.
OL,16,F"He'd written the wrong address so it
OL,17,Fwas returned to him and I never saw it
OL,18,Fbut that kind of validates me and I
OL,19,Fthink he'd be made up at the lengths
OL,20,Fwe've gone to."
