OL,6,FVolunteer Alison Bailey-Smith said it
OL,7,Fhad been a struggle at first to
OL,8,Fconvince people the property should be
OL,9,Flisted.
OL,11,FShe said: "Normally a listing might
OL,12,Fhappen for a building of historic or
OL,13,Farchitectural significance but this is
OL,14,Fto do with an artist, an artist who
OL,15,Fhas allowed his creativity to take
OL,16,Fover the building from floor to
OL,17,Fceiling.
