OL,6,F"There isn't anything like it in the
OL,7,FUK as far as we know and there's
OL,8,Fcertainly not another one that's
OL,9,Flisted so we're absolutely delighted."
OL,11,FSarah Charlesworth, listing team
OL,12,Fleader north at Historic England,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Ron's Place is a testament to
OL,14,Fthe unique artistic achievements and
OL,15,Fvision of Ron Gittins over four
OL,16,Fdecades.
