OL,6,F"The extent to which Ron's creations
OL,7,Fhave inspired action from people in
OL,8,Fthe local area to raise funds to
OL,9,Fpurchase the building and secure the
OL,10,Fsurvival of his legacy demonstrates
OL,11,Fthe value of this remarkable project
OL,12,Fand why it has earned its place on the
OL,13,FNational Heritage List for England."
